label: Charleston Yearbook, 1949-50-51
description: A report from the mayor, city council, and various governmental departments of Charleston, South Carolina for the three years spanning 1949, 1950, and 1951.  The Year Book opens with an address from the mayor, R. Goodwyn Rhett, followed by reports from various departments.
